                Dachau
            </p>
                            <p class="municipality">
                <strong>Location:</strong>
                Landsberg am Lech, Germany<br />
                            </p>
                            <div>
                This subcamp did not receive Jews until the winter of 1944-45.
            </div>
                            <style type="text/css">
.olLayerDiv{
